rows.label: qst650108_0010
rows.name: More reinforcements...

rows.label: qst650108_0020
rows.name:
This must be their last
desperate struggle, but...

rows.label: qst650108_0030
rows.name: This many is going to be tough.

rows.label: qst650108_0040
rows.name: T-elos Re:?

rows.label: qst650108_0050
rows.name: Come... I'll make it quick for you...

rows.label: qst650108_0060
rows.name: This will be your grave...

rows.label: qst650108_0070
rows.name: D-damn it!

rows.label: qst650108_0080
rows.name:
You filthy creatures... Did you
really think you could defeat me?

rows.label: qst650108_0085
rows.name: [ML:undisp ]!!

rows.label: qst650108_0090
rows.name: Whoa!

rows.label: qst650108_0100
rows.name: Merciless as ever...

rows.label: qst650108_0110
rows.name: T-elos Re:, are you alright?

rows.label: qst650108_0120
rows.name: No problem.

rows.label: qst650108_0130
rows.name: Thanks.

rows.label: qst650108_0140
rows.name:
You were a huge help,
T-elos Re:, but...

rows.label: qst650108_0150
rows.name: I wish you wouldn't be so reckless.

rows.label: qst650108_0160
rows.name: Your concern is unnecessary.

rows.label: qst650108_0170
rows.name: Battle is a Blade's true purpose.

rows.label: qst650108_0180
rows.name: You don't need to worry about me.

rows.label: qst650108_0190
rows.name: Even if that's your belief as a Driver.

rows.label: qst650108_0200
rows.name: No, but...

rows.label: qst650108_0210
rows.name:
It's impossible not to worry
about your friends, right?

rows.label: qst650108_0220
rows.name:
If you keep preaching, I'll stomp
on you like I did the last one...

rows.label: qst650108_0230
rows.name: Scary...

rows.label: qst650108_0240
rows.name:
Ah, T-elos Re: is a
particularly unique Blade.

rows.label: qst650108_0250
rows.name: A type I've never seen before...

rows.label: qst650108_0260
rows.name: But there's no doubting her skill.

rows.label: qst650108_0270
rows.name:
She is an indispensable
part of our group.

rows.label: qst650108_0280
rows.name: That's true. She's reliable.

rows.label: qst650108_0290
rows.name: We're counting on you, T-elos Re:.

rows.label: qst650108_0300
rows.name: Hmph...

rows.label: qst650108_0310
rows.name: Hahaha...

rows.label: qst650108_0320
rows.name: I wonder if we'll ever get along...?
